name: Gollumcorelib
body:
GollumCoreLib
=============


It's library for Minecraft Mod. Add functionalities :

 - Blocks Factory
 - Items Factory
 - SoundRegistery
 - Building builder
 - Logger
 - Version Checker
 - Block entity auto-spawner
 - Mod metadatas getter
 - Annotation config loader
 - Several Helper
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
